 Ok, quickly memming my gate spell, I cast it.  The seconds trickled by, the mobs were staring glassy eyed in their longing for my enchanter flesh.  I vanished.<br>
<br>
<br>
Return to PoK.  All in all a good dungeon for high level groups.  Take a cleric, a slower and some beefy tanks.  An evacer might be considered a must in this zone due to the trouble with crossing the lava at the entrance/exit.  None of  the mobs that my group encountered summoned, but that is not to say that others won't...<br>
<br>
Good luck.<br>
